body:
Hi, i recently left an aram in the champ select, the reason for that was that my league client went all black (except for my friend list, clubs, chats etc) I didnt NEED to leave but still, it would be pretty frustrating to look into a black client for more than one minute. I thought the queue wait would only be 5 minutes since i only left one game before this one, unfortunately, it was 14 minutes long.
{{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}
It would be really nice to get some information on why this happened to me, maybe i deserved it? idk
